data.description: Discover this cozy unit that is move-in ready, featuring 2 spacious bedrooms and 1 bathroom with newer flooring throughout. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen spaces, perfect for gatherings. Step outside to your private patio for a relaxing time. This FHA/VA approved unit is located in the desirable San Carlos neighborhood, conveniently situated near freeway access and within walking distance to various shopping centers across the street. HOA fees include water, and you have access to two swimming pools as well as a large playground area. It's a great unit for a small family or as a starter home
